          <rect x="167" y="55" width="40" height="6" rx="2" fill="#7e6494"/>
          <rect x="167" y="68" width="80" height="4" rx="2" fill="#d8d5cd"/>
          <rect x="167" y="92" width="96" height="40" rx="4" fill="#f1eef7"/>
          <rect x="300" y="80" width="130" height="100" rx="6" fill="#fff" stroke="#1f2330" stroke-width="0.6"/>
          <rect x="312" y="94" width="40" height="6" rx="2" fill="#3f5a93"/>
          <g stroke="#9aa0ad" stroke-width="0.6" fill="none">
            <polyline points="312 160, 332 145, 352 152, 372 130, 392 138, 412 120"/>
          </g>
          <g fill="#3f5a93">
            <circle cx="332" cy="145" r="2"/><circle cx="352" cy="152" r="2"/>
            <circle cx="372" cy="130" r="2"/><circle cx="392" cy="138" r="2"/><circle cx="412" cy="120" r="2"/>
          </g>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>What you'll get</h3>
      <div class="feature-list">
        <div class="item"><span class="lbl">A.</span><div><h4>要件・体験設計</h4><p>UXリサーチからプロト検証まで、輪郭を一緒に描きます。</p></div></div>
        <div class="item"><span class="lbl">B.</span><div><h4>モダンな実装</h4><p>TypeScript/React/Goなど、長く保守できる選択を。</p></div></div>
        <div class="item"><span class="lbl">C.</span><div><h4>QA・運用設計</h4><p>テスト自動化、観測性、リリース運用まで丁寧に。</p></div></div>
        <div class="item"><span class="lbl">D.</span><div><h4>内製化伴走</h4><p>段階的にお客様チームへ知識を移し、自走を支援。</p></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-row">
        <div class="stat"><div class="v">68<span style="font-size:18px;color:var(--ink-3);">+</span></div><div class="l">プロダクト開発実績</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="v">3.4<span style="font-size:18px;color:var(--ink-3);">m</span></div><div class="l">最短MVP期間</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="v">96<span style="font-size:18px;color:var(--ink-3);">%</span></div><div class="l">継続発注率</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 04 CONSULT -->
<section class="svc-block consult" id="consult">
